data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER! Low maintenance living in Leesburg’s premier 55+ community Arlington Ridge! GUARD GATED with an array of fantastic amenities this 2BD/2BA +DEN home sits in the perfect location with a GOLF COURSE VIEW, NEWER ROOF (2021), your choice of front or back SCREENED PORCHES, EXTENDED GARAGE and a beautiful OPEN CONCEPT! Seller is offering a home warranty with acceptable offer. Easy care tile floors run throughout the main living areas adding to the light and bright feel, making it easy to gather with family and entertain friends. A nice sized den at the front of the home gives you additional versatile space for a home office, craft room or guests! Your living area delivers arched BUILT-INS to display all of your favorite treasures and memories and there is sliding glass door access to the expansive rear lanai for indoor/outdoor living at its finest. The home chef will rave over the gorgeous kitchen, a comfortable layout makes it easy to prepare meals and there are plenty of SOLID WOOD CABINETS, stainless steel appliances, a closet pantry for ample storage and a BREAKFAST BAR for entertaining overlooking a spacious dining area with a second set of sliding glass doors. The bedrooms are split from one another providing a sanctuary in your PRIMARY SUITE with a lovely tray ceiling, WALK-IN CLOSET and private bath. Start and end your day with ease in this en-suite featuring an extended DUAL SINK VANITY with space for seating, a corner SOAKING TUB and oversized WALK-IN SHOWER! The second bedroom is also a great size with a feature wall, ceiling fan and easy access to the second full bath. The perfect outdoor space awaits in the 25x10 screened lanai, overlooking thoughtful mature landscaping highlighting this golf course lot! Jump in your golf court and explore the endless amenities this community has to offer from the lighted tennis and pickleball courts to the HEATED SWIMMING POOLS, fitness center, steam room, restaurants, movie theater and so much more! In a great location just minutes from local shopping, dining and the many area lakes with easy access to all that Central Florida has to offer. Call today to schedule your showing and live like you’re on vacation all year long!
